&lt;li&gt;Interact with key clients to understand and resolve complex issues related to the platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with our relationship management team to develop a coverage strategy for existing client relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and originate new business opportunities, whether through your own actions or in partnership with our marketing organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the sales pipeline and relationships using CRM and partner with the data team to develop and maintain internal reporting tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on the development of product and functional strategy for Flourish&lt;/li&gt;
